reviewText: I love O.A.R., and this was one of their best concerts I've seen!  The sound was fantastic, as well as the over all performance.  The incredibly quality really makes the concert much more amazing.  If you're a fan of O.A.R., this is a great disc to own.  It's definately something I watch over and over.
